-2025idbuzzcandywhiteoverenergeticorange.jpg\" data-full-width=\"2000\" data-image-id=\"ci02f53768900025cf\" data-image-slug=\"Large-18246-2025ID.BuzzCandyWhiteoverEnergeticOrange\" data-public-id=\"MjEzMTM3NDc1NTc1NDkwMzk3\" data-title=\"2025 Volkswagen ID.Buzz\"\u003e\u003c/phx-gallery-image\u003e\u003cphx-gallery-image data-caption-html=\"\u0026lt;p\u0026gt;2025 Volkswagen ID.Buzz\u0026lt;/p\u0026gt;\" data-full-height=\"1334\" data-full-src=\"https://www.autoblog.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cfl_progressive%2Ch_2000%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_2000/MjEzMTM3NDc1MzA3MDU0NTQz/large-18243-2025idbuzzcandywhiteoverenergeticorange.jpg\" data-full-width=\"2000\" data-image-id=\"ci02f53768400025cf\" data-image-slug=\"Large-18243-2025ID.BuzzCandyWhiteoverEnergeticOrange\" data-public-id=\"MjEzMTM3NDc1MzA3MDU0NTQz\" data-title=\"2025 Volkswagen ID.Buzz\"\u003e\u003c/phx-gallery-image\u003e\u003cphx-gallery-image data-caption-html=\"\u0026lt;p\u0026gt;2025 Volkswagen ID.Buzz\u0026lt;/p\u0026gt;\" data-full-height=\"1334\" data-full-src=\"https://www.autoblog.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cfl_progressive%2Ch_2000%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_2000/MjEzMTM3NDc1NTc1NzUyNTQx/large-18260-2025idbuzzcandywhiteoverenergeticorange.jpg\" data-full-width=\"2000\" data-image-id=\"ci02f53768e00025cf\" data-image-slug=\"Large-18260-2025ID.BuzzCandyWhiteoverEnergeticOrange\" data-public-id=\"MjEzMTM3NDc1NTc1NzUyNTQx\" data-title=\"2025 Volkswagen ID.Buzz\"\u003e\u003c/phx-gallery-image\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003ch2 id=\"2025-volkswagen-id-buzz\"\u003e2025 Volkswagen ID.Buzz\u003c/h2\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cfigure itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/ImageObject\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://www.autoblog.com/.image/ar_16:9%2Cc_fill%2Ccs_srgb%2Cfl_progressive%2Ch_406%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_620/MjEzMTM3NDc1NTc1NzUyMTQz/large-18275-2025idbuzzcandywhiteoverenergeticorange.jpg\" alt=\"Large-18275-2025ID.BuzzCandyWhiteoverEnergeticOrange\" itemprop=\"image\" loading=\"lazy\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003eIn our research, we discovered discounts nationwide, although not as low as the models found in Colorado. Discounts ranged from a few hundred dollars to a few thousand across trim levels. The large selection available for sale at or below MSRP combined with infrequent sightings is also significant, indicating that the ID.Buzz isn’t selling very well. Also notable is the fact that few dealerships are marking up the ID.Buzz. Only new cars in high demand get that dubious honor. \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eWhat could likely be significant price hurdles are the potential removal of the $7,500 federal tax credit for new EV purchases and a 25 percent tariff on imported vehicles imposed by the Trump administration. Either one or both measures could put the ID.Buzz even further out of reach for potential buyers. These discounts and incentives make now the right time to buy an ID.Buzz if you’re in the market for a family EV with space and style.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cfigure itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/ImageObject\"\u003e\u003cphoenix-picture\u003e\u003ca\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource type=\"image/webp\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1240px) 700px, (min-width: 675px) 620px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-srcset=\"https://www.autoblog.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_380/MjEzMTM4MDA5MjI1MTc2NTI3/2025-volkswagen-idbuzz.webp 380w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_620/MjEzMTM4MDA5MjI1MTc2NTI3/2025-volkswagen-idbuzz.webp 620w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_700/MjEzMTM4MDA5MjI1MTc2NTI3/2025-volkswagen-idbuzz.webp 700w\"/\u003e\u003csource sizes=\"(min-width: 1240px) 700px, (min-width: 675px) 620px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-srcset=\"https://www.autoblog.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_380/MjEzMTM4MDA5MjI1MTc2NTI3/2025-volkswagen-idbuzz.jpg 380w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_620/MjEzMTM4MDA5MjI1MTc2NTI3/2025-volkswagen-idbuzz.jpg 620w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_700/MjEzMTM4MDA5MjI1MTc2NTI3/2025-volkswagen-idbuzz.jpg 700w\"/\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"2025 Volkswagen ID.Buzz\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.autoblog.com/.image/t_share/MjEzMTM4MDA5MjI1MTc2NTI3/2025-volkswagen-idbuzz.jpg\" data-src=\"https://www.autoblog.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_700/MjEzMTM4MDA5MjI1MTc2NTI3/2025-volkswagen-idbuzz.jpg\" height=\"4805\" width=\"7204\" srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7\" itemprop=\"contentUrl url\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/phoenix-picture\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003e\u003cp itemprop=\"caption\"\u003e2025 Volkswagen ID.Buzz\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp itemprop=\"author\"\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://media.vw.com/en-us/models/id-buzz\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" onclick=\"return phoenixTrackClickEvent(this, event);\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eVolkswagen\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003ch2 id=\"final-thoughts\"\u003eFinal thoughts\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cp\u003eWe think the new ID.Buzz is a phenomenal vehicle in terms of style, space, and driving fun, but the price is hard to stomach. Discounts bring down the price of entry, and it’s possible that there’s room for negotiation with dealerships that aren’t offering discounts right off the bat.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe ID.Buzz makes a compelling case for an electric family vehicle, but waning interest in EVs doesn’t help its case. Discounts certainly make it more compelling, but you’d better move quickly.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cem\u003eLove reading Autoblog? Sign up for our weekly newsletter to get exclusive articles, insider insights, and the latest updates delivered right to your inbox. \u003ca href=\"https://na01.safelinks.protection.outloo